Deputy President David Mabuza answers questions in the National Council of Provinces. CAPE TOWN - Deputy President David Mabuza was in the National Council of Provinces (NCOP) on Thursday, for oral replies to questions by the NCOP permanent delegates. WATCH: President Ramaphosa Q&A in the NCOP Some of the topics covered by the questions posed to Deputy President are whether the government has put any critical asset maintenance strategies in place at Eskom, the sewage situation in Emfuleni, and rural and township empowerment.